Package au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.definition

Interface NodeDefinition

All Known Subinterfaces:
ChildDefinition, ChoiceDefinition, ElementDefinition, ResourceDefinition
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultChoiceDefinition, DefaultCompositeDefinition, DefaultPrimitiveDefinition, DefaultResourceDefinition
public interface NodeDefinition
Base class for FHIR-like schema definitions. The schema is capable or representing a subset all FHIR schema concepts such as elements, choices, and resources.
